{"title":"窗口（歌词）","authors":["李平安"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":7,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口（歌词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李平安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当中午时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我望着医院的窗口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个熟悉的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"频频向我招手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是我的亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔赴了抗非典一线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们分手的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相约这样见面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遏住了非典凶焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病人一批批出院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么盼望亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早一天回家团圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是那熟悉的窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不见熟悉的身影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少白衣战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然忙碌匆匆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿凋谢了又开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人再没有回来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我日夜思念那窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将永远把您等待！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}